  • 所有已实现的接口:

    public class PanoramicView
extends android.opengl.GLSurfaceView
implements android.opengl.GLSurfaceView.Renderer, PGesture.OnGestureListener, PDeviceMotionSensor.DeviceMotionListener
    A view container where OpenGL ES graphics can be drawn on screen. This view can also be used to capture touch events, such as a user interacting with drawn objects.
